{"tid":866105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】重慶大廈兩女打鬥 1人遭割頸插腹","createTime":"2018-10-17T15:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T15:47:27.000Z","uid":11148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d69affb58f5e577267a1697e45886bc0bee0117","tid":866105,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181017/58804082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58804082&d=7UX%2BBvJQWLS7krpEBAQuQMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=7f5c8939\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181017%2F58804082&h=769cdfa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181017/58804082</a><br />\n尖沙咀彌敦道36-44號重慶大廈，早上近11時，警方接獲報案，指<span style=\"color: red;\">兩名非洲烏干達女子因事大打出手</span>，其中一名女子Sophie以玻璃樽碎片作武器，襲擊另一名女子Lisa。救護員接報到場，Lisa已倒卧地上，她頸及腹部被割傷，地面遺下大灘鮮血，昏迷不醒，另一名女同鄉Sophie則清醒，衣衫染血，報稱不適，兩人一併由救護車送院治理。警方經初步調查，Sophie涉嫌傷人被拘捕，案件交油尖警區刑事調查隊5隊跟進。<br />\n據悉，今早8時許兩女偕友人，在重慶大廈地下坐在舖頭對開的枱椅飲酒傾談，其間二人為事爭執，其中一人情緒激動，走入舖頭內擸刀揮舞，被友人制止，其後有人擸起枱上玻璃樽掟向對方不果，玻璃樽掟落地爆裂，有人執起玻璃碎片，向事主割頸插腹，事主當場淌血，行了約10米便不支倒地，昏迷不醒血泊中，傷人者未有逃走，坐在一旁，救護員接報到場，為昏迷傷者包紥後急送院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181017/large/1539769670_419d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181017%2Flarge%2F1539769670_419d.jpg&h=666d5af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nwakanda forever<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a4286840267c363b421a8168aaaaf58b1eddd9","tid":866105,"uid":208364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁狼死"},{"pid":"7306edd60b37c68bc106c0e48dc211a0ab2eb26b","tid":866105,"uid":56999,"